about.description: Python tools for EPICS Process Database
about.summary: Python tools for EPICS Process Database

name: epics-pypdb
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "epics-pypdb" %}
{% set version = "0.1.4" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://github.com/pcdshub/epics-pypdb/archive/{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 3e402b8f946c528257203649dc1e33ac49d56773d6b1ff7df40407a478cf9900

build:
  noarch: python
  number: 0
  script: "{{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv"

requirements:
  host:
    - python
    - pip
    - ply
  run:
    - python
    - ply

test:
  commands:
    - python -m nose pyPDB

  requires:
    - nose

about:
  home: https://github.com/pcdshub/epics-pypdb
  license: EPICS Open
  license_family: Other
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: 'Python tools for EPICS Process Database'
  description: |
    Python tools for EPICS Process Database
  dev_url: https://github.com/pcdshub/epics-pypdb

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - hhslepicka
